## Authentication Routes (4 routes)

| Route | Method | Auth | Purpose |
|-------|--------|------|---------|
| `/api/auth/set-role` | GET | ❌ | Get user type & setup status |
| `/api/user/profile` | GET | ✅ | Get current user profile |
| `/api/clerk/webhook` | POST | ❌ | Clerk auth events |
| `/api/verification/school` | POST | ❌ | Verify school code |

**Protected:** 1/4 (25%)
**Public:** 3/4 (webhooks, setup, verification)

