## Response Format Standards

### Success Response
```typescript
{
  success: true,
  data: T
}
```

### Error Response
```typescript
{
  success: false,
  error: string
}
```

### Pagination
```typescript
{
  success: true,
  data: T[],
  pagination: {
    page: number,
    limit: number,
    total: number,
    totalPages: number
  }
}
```

